query {
  ~version: 
}

docs {
  ## Get Workflow Stages of a Purchase Request
  ดึงขั้นตอนการอนุมัติที่กำหนดไว้สำหรับใบขอซื้อในหน่วยธุรกิจ แสดงลำดับขั้นตอนอนุมัติที่ใบขอซื้อต้องผ่าน Returns only items pending the requesting user's action / แสดงเฉพาะรายการที่รอการดำเนินการของผู้ใช้ปัจจุบัน

  Retrieves the approval workflow stages configured for purchase requests in the business unit, showing the sequence of approval steps (e.g., HOD, Finance Controller, GM) that a purchase request must pass through.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |

  ### Query Parameters
  | Name | Type | Required | Default | Description |
  |------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
  | `version` | string | No | latest | API version |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  - **Permission key**: `procurement.purchase_request:view`
  - **Roles**: Requestor, HOD, Purchase, Approval

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "workflowStages": [
        { "stage": 1, "role": "HOD", "label": "Head of Department" },
        { "stage": 2, "role": "FC", "label": "Finance Controller" },
        { "stage": 3, "role": "GM", "label": "General Manager" }
      ]
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 401 | Missing or invalid Bearer token |
  | 403 | User lacks `procurement.purchase_request:view` permission |
  | 404 | Workflow stages not found for this business unit |
}

params:path {
  bu_code: {{bu_code}}
}
